FBIS3-39721 "drweu035_b_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-035 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Feb 1994 BENELUX Belgium Delcroix Denies Claes Statement LD2102150594 Brussels Radio Vlaanderen International in English 1400 GMT 21 Feb 94 LD2102150594 Brussels Radio Vlaanderen International Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Belgium's Defence Minister Leo Delcroix has denied that our country is sending troops to Sarajevo. Earlier today Foreign Affairs Minister Willy Claes said that Belgian soldiers would be transferred from Croatia to the Bosnian capital. But Mr. Delcroix has denied this, explaining that Mr. Claes, who is currently travelling through Africa, was wrongly informed.
